Package smarthome.persistence.mem

Class ActuatorModelRepositoryMemImpl

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.mem.ActuatorModelRepositoryMemImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<ActuatorModelName, ActuatorModel>, IActuatorModelRepository
public class ActuatorModelRepositoryMemImpl extends Object implements IActuatorModelRepository
The ActuatorModelRepositoryMemImpl class represents a repository for managing ActuatorModel entities. It provides methods to save, retrieve, and manipulate ActuatorModel objects. This repository is backed by an in-memory HashMap data structure.

ActuatorModelName representing the identity of Sensor entities. ActuatorModel representing ActuatorModel entities.
